<text><body>
<lb n="0464b17"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0464b18"/>
<lb n="0464b19"/><head type="no">No. 1313</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0464b20"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0464001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本</note>佛說救拔&CB04059;口餓鬼陀羅尼經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0464b21"/>
<lb n="0464b22"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0464002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（開府…門））四十一字＝（（大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智））十一字【宋】【元】，（（唐三藏沙門大廣智））八字【明】【甲】</note><note n="0464002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（（開府…門））四十一字＝（（大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智））十一字【宋】【元】，＝（（唐三藏沙門大廣智））八字【明】【甲】</note><app n="0464002" word-count="41"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0464b23"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空謚大鑒
<lb n="0464b24"/>正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">唐三藏沙門大廣智</rdg></app>
<lb n="0464b25"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0464b26"/><p>爾時世尊。在迦毘羅城尼<note n="0464003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">俱＝拘【三】【甲】</note><note n="0464003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">俱＝拘【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0464003"><lem>俱</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">拘</rdg></app>律那僧伽藍所。
<lb n="0464b27"/>與諸比丘并諸菩薩無數眾會。前後圍遶而
<lb n="0464b28"/>為說法。爾時阿難獨居靜處念所受法。即於
<lb n="0464b29"/>其夜三更已後。見一餓鬼名曰焰口。其形醜
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1313.0464c" n="0464c"/>
<lb n="0464c01"/>陋身體枯瘦。口中火然咽如針鋒。頭髮<note n="0464004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蓬＝髼【三】＊</note><note n="0464004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蓬＝髼【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0464004"><lem>蓬</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">髼</rdg></app>亂
<lb n="0464c02"/>爪牙長利甚可怖畏。住阿難前白阿難言。&CB00230;
<lb n="0464c03"/>後三日汝命將盡。即便生<note n="0464005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">於＝此【三】【甲】</note><note n="0464005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">於＝此【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0464005"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">此</rdg></app>餓鬼之中。是時
<lb n="0464c04"/>阿難聞此語已。心生惶怖問餓鬼言。若我死
<lb n="0464c05"/>後生餓鬼者。行何方便得免斯苦。</p>
<lb n="0464c06"/><p>爾時餓鬼白阿難<note n="0464006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝曰【三】【甲】</note><note n="0464006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＝曰【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0464006"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">曰</rdg></app>。汝於明日。若能布施百
<lb n="0464c07"/>千那由他&M010527;河沙數餓鬼。并百千婆羅門仙
<lb n="0464c08"/>等。以摩伽陀國所用之斛。各施一斛飲食。并
<lb n="0464c09"/>及為我供養三寶。汝得增壽。令我離於餓鬼
<lb n="0464c10"/>之苦得生天上。阿難見此焰口餓鬼。身形羸
<lb n="0464c11"/>瘦枯燋極醜。口中火然咽如針鋒。頭髮<app type="＊" source="0464004"><lem>蓬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">髼</rdg></app>亂
<lb n="0464c12"/><note n="0464007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">毛爪＝爪牙【三】【甲】</note><note n="0464007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">毛爪＝爪牙【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0464007"><lem>毛爪</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">爪牙</rdg></app>長利。又聞如是不順之語。甚大驚怖身
<lb n="0464c13"/>毛皆&CB00594;。即從座起疾至佛所。五體投地頂禮
<lb n="0464c14"/>佛足。身體<note n="0464008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">戰＝顫【三】</note><note n="0464008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">戰＝顫【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0464008"><lem>戰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">顫</rdg></app>慄而白佛言願救我苦所以者
<lb n="0464c15"/>何。我住靜處念所<note n="0464009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">授＝受【三】【甲】</note><note n="0464009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">授＝受【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0464009"><lem>授</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">受</rdg></app>法。見焰口餓鬼而語我
<lb n="0464c16"/>言。汝過三日必當命盡生餓鬼中。我即問言
<lb n="0464c17"/>云何令我得免斯苦。餓鬼答言。汝今若能施
<lb n="0464c18"/>於百千那由他&M010527;河沙數餓鬼。及百千婆羅
<lb n="0464c19"/>門仙等種種飲食。汝得增壽。世尊我今云何
<lb n="0464c20"/>能辦若干餓鬼仙人等食。</p>
<lb n="0464c21"/><p>爾時世尊告阿難言。汝今勿怖我有方便。令
<lb n="0464c22"/>汝能施若干百千&M010527;河沙餓鬼。及諸婆羅門
<lb n="0464c23"/>仙等種種飲食。勿生憂惱。</p>
<lb n="0464c24"/><p>佛告阿難有陀羅尼。名曰無量威德自在光
<lb n="0464c25"/>明<note n="0464010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔殊〕－【甲】</note><app n="0464010"><lem>殊</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>勝妙力。若有誦此陀羅尼者。即能充足
<lb n="0464c26"/>俱胝那由他百千&M010527;河沙數餓鬼。及婆羅門
<lb n="0464c27"/>仙等上妙飲食。如是等眾乃至一一。皆得摩
<lb n="0464c28"/>伽陀國所用之斛七七斛食。阿難我於前世
<lb n="0464c29"/>作婆羅門。於觀<note n="0464011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世音＝自在【三】【甲】</note><note n="0464011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世音＝自在【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0464011"><lem>世音</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">自在</rdg></app>菩薩所。及世間自在威
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1313.0465a" n="0465a"/>
<lb n="0465a01"/>德如來所。受此陀羅尼故。能散施與無量餓
<lb n="0465a02"/>鬼及諸仙等種種飲食。令諸餓鬼解脫苦身
<lb n="0465a03"/>得生天上。阿難汝今受持。福德壽命皆得增
<lb n="0465a04"/>長。爾時世尊即為阿難。說陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0465a05"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0465001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">那謨＝曩莫【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">那謨＝曩莫【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465001"><lem>那謨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">曩莫</rdg></app>薩<note n="0465002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＋（無可反下同）【元】，（無可切下同）【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465002"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;無可反下同</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;無可切下同</rdg></app>怛<note n="0465003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">他＋（引）夾註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">他＋（引）夾註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465003"><lem>他</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">他<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app><note n="0465004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00617;多引＝&CB00617;跢引一【宋】【元】，&CB00858;跢引一【明】</note><note n="0465004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00617;多引＝&CB00617;跢引一【宋】【元】，＝&CB00858;跢引一【明】</note><app n="0465004"><lem>&CB00617;多<note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&CB00617;跢引一</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00858;跢引一</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note n="0465005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盧＝路引【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盧＝路引【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465005"><lem>盧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">路引</rdg></app>枳<note n="0465006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">帝＋（二）夾註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">帝＋（二）夾註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465006"><lem>帝</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">帝<note place="inline">二</note></rdg></app><note n="0465007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唵參婆囉參婆囉吽＝唵引三三去跋羅三拔羅吽引四【宋】【元】，唵引三三去聲跋羅三跋羅吽引四【明】【甲】</note><note n="0465007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唵參婆囉參婆囉吽＝唵引三三去跋羅三拔羅吽引四【宋】【元】，＝唵引三三去聲跋羅三跋羅吽引四【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465007"><lem>唵
<lb n="0465a06"/>參婆囉參婆囉吽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">唵引三三去跋羅三拔羅吽引四</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">唵引三三去聲跋羅三跋羅吽引四</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0465a07"/><p>佛告阿難。若有善男子善女人。欲求長壽福
<lb n="0465a08"/>德增榮。速能滿足檀波羅蜜。每於晨朝及一
<lb n="0465a09"/>切時悉無障礙。取一淨器盛以淨水。置少<note n="0465008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飯＝飲【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯＝飲【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465008"><lem>飯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">飲</rdg></app>
<lb n="0465a10"/>&CB00595;及諸餅<note n="0465009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＝飯【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食＝飯【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465009"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">飯</rdg></app>等。以右手<note n="0465010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">加＝按【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">加＝按【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465010"><lem>加</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">按</rdg></app>器。誦前陀羅尼
<lb n="0465a11"/>滿七遍。然後稱四如來名號。</p>
<lb n="0465a12"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0465011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（南謨多寶如來）＋曩【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（南謨多寶如來）＋曩【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465011"><lem>曩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">南謨多寶如來曩</rdg></app>謨<note n="0465012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婆＋（去）夾註【宋】【元】，（去聲）【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0465012"><lem>婆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">婆<note place="inline">去</note></rdg><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">婆去聲</rdg></app>&CB00344;&CB00085;<note n="0465013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">帝＋（一）夾註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">帝＋（一）夾註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465013"><lem>帝</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">帝<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0465014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔枳孃二合〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔枳孃二合〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465014"><lem>枳孃<note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>部<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0465a13"/><note n="0465015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多＝哆【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多＝哆【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465015"><lem>多</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">哆</rdg></app>囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0465016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（野）＋怛【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（野）＋怛【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465016"><lem>怛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">野怛</rdg></app><note n="0465017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">他＋（引）【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0465017" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>他＋（引）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0465017"><lem>他</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">他引</rdg></app>孽<note n="0465018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多也此云多寶如來＝跢引野二【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多也此云多寶如來＝跢引野二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465018"><lem>多也<note place="inline">此云多寶如來</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">跢引野二</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0465a14"/><p>由稱多寶如來名號加持故。能破一切諸鬼。
<lb n="0465a15"/>多生已來慳&CB00385;惡<note n="0465019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">業＋（罪障消滅）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">業＋（罪障消滅）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465019"><lem>業</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">業罪障消滅</rdg></app>。即得福德圓滿。</p>
<lb n="0465a16"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0465020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">那＝南謨妙色身如來曩【三】，曩【甲】</note><note n="0465020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">那＝南謨妙色身如來曩【宋】【元】【明】，＝曩【甲】</note><app n="0465020"><lem>那</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">南謨妙色身如來曩</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">曩</rdg></app>謨婆&CB00344;<note n="0465021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝縛【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00085;＝縛【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465021"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">縛</rdg></app><note n="0465022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">帝＋（一）【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0465022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">帝＋（一）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0465022"><lem>帝</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">帝一</rdg></app>素嚕<note n="0465023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">波引耶＝二合播引野【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">波引耶＝二合播引野【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465023"><lem>波<note place="inline">引</note>耶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">二合播引野</rdg></app>怛他&CB00344;<note n="0465024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">哆＝跢【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">哆＝跢【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465024"><lem>哆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">跢</rdg></app>
<lb n="0465a17"/>野<note place="inline"><note n="0465025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此云南無妙色身如來＝二【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此云南無妙色身如來＝二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465025"><lem>此云南無妙色身如來</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0465a18"/><p>由稱妙色身如來名號加持故。能破諸鬼醜
<lb n="0465a19"/>陋惡形。即得色相具足。</p>
<lb n="0465a20"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0465026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（南謨廣博身如來）＋曩【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（南謨廣博身如來）＋曩【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465026"><lem>曩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">南謨廣博身如來曩</rdg></app><note n="0465027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謨＋（引）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謨＋（引）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465027"><lem>謨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">謨引</rdg></app>婆&CB00344;&CB00085;<app type="＊" source="0465022"><lem>帝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">帝一</rdg></app>尾<note n="0465028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（&CB00425;囉…來））二十五字＝（（補羅&CB00344;引怛囉二合引野怛他引孽跢引野二））十八字【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（（&CB00425;囉…來））二十五字＝（（補羅&CB00344;引怛囉二合引野怛他引孽跢引野二））十八字【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465028" word-count="25"><lem>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00344;&CB00256;孽多怛
<lb n="0465a21"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>也怛他孽多也<note place="inline">此云廣博身如來</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">補羅&CB00344;引怛囉二合引野怛他引孽跢引野二</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0465a22"/><p>由稱廣博身如來名號加持故。能令諸鬼咽
<lb n="0465a23"/>喉寬大。所施之食恣意充飽。</p>
<lb n="0465a24"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0465029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（南謨離怖如來）＋曩【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（南謨離怖如來）＋曩【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465029"><lem>曩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">南謨離怖如來曩</rdg></app>謨<app type="＊" source="0465012"><lem>婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">婆去聲</rdg></app>&CB00344;&CB00085;<app type="＊" source="0465022"><lem>帝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">帝一</rdg></app>阿<note place="inline"><note n="0465030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＋（聲）【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465030"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">上聲</rdg></app></note>婆<note place="inline"><note n="0465031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＋（聲）【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465031"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">去聲</rdg></app></note>孕迦<note n="0465032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉也＝囉引野【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉也＝囉引野【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465032"><lem>囉也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">囉引野</rdg></app>怛
<lb n="0465a25"/><note n="0465033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">他＋（去）【宋】【元】，（去聲）【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465033"><lem>他</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">他去</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">他去聲</rdg></app>&CB00617;<note n="0465034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多也此云離怖畏如來＝哆引野二【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多也此云離怖畏如來＝哆引野二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465034"><lem>多也<note place="inline">此云離怖畏如來</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">哆引野二</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0465a26"/><p>由稱離怖畏如來名號加持故。能令諸鬼一
<lb n="0465a27"/>切恐怖悉皆除滅離餓鬼趣。佛告阿難若族
<lb n="0465a28"/>姓<note n="0465035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善男子等既＝子等【三】，子等既【甲】</note><note n="0465035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善男子等既＝子等【宋】【元】【明】，＝子等既【甲】</note><app n="0465035"><lem>善男子等。既</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">子等</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">子等既</rdg></app>稱四如來名號加持已。彈指
<lb n="0465a29"/>七遍。取於食器於淨地上。展臂瀉之。作此施
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1313.0465b" n="0465b"/>
<lb n="0465b01"/>已。於其四方有百千那由他&M010527;河沙數餓鬼。
<lb n="0465b02"/>前<note n="0465036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">各＋（各）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">各＋（各）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465036"><lem>各</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">各各</rdg></app>有摩伽陀國七七斛食。受此食已悉皆
<lb n="0465b03"/>飽滿。是諸<note n="0465037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鬼等悉＝餓鬼悉等【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鬼等悉＝餓鬼悉等【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465037"><lem>鬼等悉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">餓鬼悉等</rdg></app>捨鬼身生於天上。</p>
<lb n="0465b04"/><p>阿難若有比丘比丘尼優婆塞優婆夷。常以
<lb n="0465b05"/>此<note n="0465038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">密＝真【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0465038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">密＝真【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0465038"><lem>密</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">真</rdg></app>言及四如來名號。加持食<note n="0465039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">施＋（餓）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">施＋（餓）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465039"><lem>施</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">施餓</rdg></app>鬼。便能
<lb n="0465b06"/>具足無量福德。則同供養百千俱胝如來功
<lb n="0465b07"/>德等無差別。壽命延長增益色力善根具足。
<lb n="0465b08"/>一切非人夜叉羅剎。諸惡鬼神不敢侵害。又
<lb n="0465b09"/>能成就無量福德壽命。若欲施諸婆羅門仙
<lb n="0465b10"/>等。以淨飲食滿盛一器。即以前<app type="＊" source="0465038"><lem>密</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">真</rdg></app>言加持二
<lb n="0465b11"/>七遍。投於淨流水中。如是作已。即為以天
<lb n="0465b12"/><note n="0465040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仙＝諸【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465040"><lem>仙</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">諸</rdg></app>美妙<note n="0465041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＝飲【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之＝飲【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465041"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">飲</rdg></app>食。供養百千俱胝&M010527;河沙數婆
<lb n="0465b13"/>羅門仙。彼諸仙人得加持食故。<note n="0465042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以密言＝以&CB00057;【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以密言＝以&CB00057;【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465042"><lem>以密言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">以&CB00057;</rdg></app>威德。
<lb n="0465b14"/>各各成就根本所願諸善功德。各各同時發
<lb n="0465b15"/>誓願言。願<note n="0465043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝施【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是＝施【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465043"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">施</rdg></app>食人<note n="0465044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令壽＝壽命【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">令壽＝壽命【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465044"><lem>令壽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">壽命</rdg></app>延長色力安樂。又
<lb n="0465b16"/>令其人心所見聞正解清淨。具足成就梵天
<lb n="0465b17"/>威德。行梵天行。又同供養百千&M010527;河沙如來
<lb n="0465b18"/>功德。一切冤讎不能侵害。若比丘比丘尼優
<lb n="0465b19"/>婆塞優婆夷。若欲供養佛法僧寶。應以香華
<lb n="0465b20"/>及淨飲食。以前<app type="＊" source="0465038"><lem>密</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">真</rdg></app>言加持二十一遍奉獻三
<lb n="0465b21"/>寶。是善男子<note n="0465045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（及）＋善【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（及）＋善【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465045"><lem>善</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">及善</rdg></app>女人。則成以天餚&CB00498;上味。
<lb n="0465b22"/>奉獻供養滿十方<note n="0465046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（世）＋界【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（世）＋界【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465046"><lem>界</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">世界</rdg></app>佛法僧寶。亦為讚歎勸
<lb n="0465b23"/>請隨喜功德。&M010527;為諸佛憶念稱讚。諸天善神
<lb n="0465b24"/>&M010527;來擁護。即為滿足檀波羅蜜。阿難汝隨我
<lb n="0465b25"/>語。如法修行廣宣流布。令諸眾生普得見聞
<lb n="0465b26"/>獲無量福。是名救焰口餓鬼及苦眾生陀羅
<lb n="0465b27"/>尼經。以是名字汝當奉持。一切大眾及阿難
<lb n="0465b28"/>等。聞佛說已一心信受歡喜奉行。</p>
